{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01JWsqB1minTwQqYZvxbUh3g","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Oracle passes. Here's what was done:\n\n**Root cause:** The running Elasticsearch StatefulSet (deployed by prior stages) had no file realm configured — no volume mount for file-realm credentials and no `xpack.security.authc.realms.file` setting in `elasticsearch.yml`. The `user-provided-file-realm` secret holding `report-user` was never visible to Elasticsearch.\n\n**Fix applied:**\n\n1. **Merged `user-provided-file-realm` into `es-file-realm-aggregate`** — concatenated `users` and `users_roles` from both secrets, keeping both `ops-user` (superuser) and `report-user` (viewer) in the aggregate secret.\n\n2. **Enabled file realm in the ConfigMap** — added `xpack.security.authc.realms.file.file1.order: 0` and `xpack.security.authc.realms.native.native1.order: 1` to `es-config`.\n\n3. **Patched the StatefulSet** — added the `file-realm` volume (sourced from `es-file-realm-aggregate`) and three `subPath` mounts for `users`, `users_roles`, and `roles.yml` into the Elasticsearch container.\n\n4. **Rolling restart** — applied changes without downtime; all 3 pods cycled one at a time.\n\n5. **Seeded `app-data` index** — the precondition's seed step hadn't run on this inherited cluster, so the index was missing; created it so `report-user` (viewer role) can read it.\n\nOracle confirms: file realm merge verified, `ops-user` and `report-user` both authenticate, cluster is green."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":426,"cache_read_input_tokens":56232,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":426},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"fdc5865e-b097-464b-9957-7edb5f96d728","uuid":"a2bf9241-b342-43b6-a3c8-aa1f12fe85b4","request_id":"req_011CcfrQU29ePkj34xkNvmjJ"}
